	<h1>One man's story: skilled, blue collar and suddenly destitute</h1>

	<blockquote>
		<h3></h3>
	</blockquote>

	<p>
		
			
			By <a href="http://www.tampabay.com/writers/will-van-sant">Will Van Sant</a>, Times Staff Writer
<br />
		
	In Print: Sunday, May 31, 2009

	</p>

	<hr size="1" noshade="noshade"/>

	
		
		
			
				
					
						
							
						



